    "description": "A rock-paper-scissor style turn-based fighting game.<br>Practice with bot or challenge your friend to a duel!<br>In each turn, both players present their option!<br>There are 3 option available which are<br><strong>Charge</strong> a charge is requires to be able to do a fireball.<br><strong>Fireball</strong> If this hits a charging opponent you win!<br><strong>Block</strong> this can negate fireball however....<br>I lied! there are actually 4 options!<br><strong>Big fireball</strong> this requires 3 charges this beats anything except itself.<br>Here is a rock-paper-scissor chart for reference<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094590/extras/a000967ecf411a1818b39c451c802743.avif?t=1722336971\" width=500 height=500 /></span><br><br>Remember! always charge on first turn! since both players cannot do fireball so there is no need to block.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094590/extras/6d1fe04846ed9754449a0d292713e14e.avif?t=1722336971\" width=510 height=436 /></span><br>Happy TobPaCharge!",
